properties.description: Stainless Steel/Black 4-Burner Liquid Propane Gas Grill with 1 Side Burner
properties.full_description: The Huntington 4-burner gas grill is designed to give you the best results and delicious food every time. With a design-engineered cooking system that features stainless steel tube burners, a stainless steel cooking system, a stainless steel cook box with cast aluminum end caps, and porcelain-coated cast iron cooking grids, this grill will give you even heat and a consistent cooking experience. The grill is as stylish as it is durable featuring a double-walled stainless steel lid with cast aluminum end caps, black painted side shelves with stainless steel fascias, and a black painted steel cart design. The 10,000 BTU flush mounted side burner gives you extra cooking versatility, allowing you to prepare delicious side dishes or warm up your favorite BBQ sauce. Other features include Linear Flow™ valves, a Sure-Lite™ electronic ignition, Accu-Temp™ lid thermometer, and removable grease pan. Proudly made in North America and featuring North American-sourced steel and a strong warranty to back it all up, this grill is designed to last and perform in your backyard for years to come!
